description:
We present the bloopers, outtakes, behind the scenes, and lost footage from the critically acclaimed movie CABO: DAY OF THE DEAD
Each night we got together and created a video diary of what it is really like on a location bondage set. Never before seen footage of Christina Carter, Dana DeArmond trying to act, and much more. Want to know what really happens on a bondage set?
Then check out this bonus update, it's that fun.
